# The Power BI project (NHANES.pbip + .SemanticModel + .Report) IS versioned so
# hand-built report pages are tracked. The generator seeds it; after that you
# own it (the generator refuses to overwrite without --force). Note: the
# semantic model bakes in an absolute exports/ path — on a new machine, edit the
# ExportsFolder parameter in Power Query (or re-run the generator with --force).
#
# Only Power BI Desktop's per-user/local/cache files are ignored — these are
# machine-specific or contain a data cache and cause churn:
**/.pbi/
**/*.abf
**/diagramLayout.json
**/semanticModelDiagramLayout.json
**/unappliedChanges.json
